<br>
Nope, it's impossible to run. In order to do the highest end stuff you need a lot of people equipped in high end equipment.  You don't get 100 people in top gear by doing things casually.  You can have some people with some of the best stuff in the game.  That's not enough though, you need a LOT of people equipped with the best they possibly can.  You can have a successful guild, but you will never, ever be able to do the top encounters because you simply won't have enough people equipped well enough to do it.   <p>-Tain<BR>
